# Project Overview

## ComfyUI LLM Party

from the most basic LLM multi-tool call, role setting to quickly build your own exclusive AI assistant, to the industry-specific word vector RAG and GraphRAG to localize the management of the industry knowledge base;

from a single agent pipeline, to the construction of complex agent-agent radial interaction mode;

from the access to their own social APP (QQ, Feishu, Discord) required by individual users, to the one-stop LLM + TTS + ComfyUI workflow required by streaming media workers;

from the simple start of the first LLM application required by ordinary students; to the various parameter debugging interfaces commonly used by scientific researchers, model adaptation.

All of this, you can find the answer in ComfyUI LLM Party.
